article.description: — Jamal Bieniemy had 23 points as UTEP beat Western New Mexico 85-57 on Tuesday night in a season opener.
article.headline: Bieniemy carries UTEP over Western New Mexico 85-57
article.linkText: Bieniemy carries UTEP over Western New Mexico 85-57
article.story: EL PASO, Texas -- — Jamal Bieniemy had 23 points as UTEP beat Western New Mexico 85-57 on Tuesday night in a season opener. Keonte Kennedy had 11 points for UTEP. Tony Avalos had 14 points for the Mustangs. Dylan Arnette added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
